{"tid":1522931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎睇片，慎防炒車！！！臥底事件重組推理！！！黑警臥底可恥！！！","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:29:41.000Z","uid":263230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1420ab936361a8a001780f7adc42bcecdfb94c3d","tid":1522931,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"先睇： <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10217964721383320&amp;id=1643611956\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10217964721383320%26id%3D1643611956&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=378c0677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10217964721383320&amp;id=1643611956</a><br />\n<br />\n然後入面有兩條：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157151750789340&amp;id=598124339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157151750789340%26id%3D598124339&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=21e0dd50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157151750789340&amp;id=598124339</a><br />\n<br />\n之後：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3076047092436334/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F3076047092436334%2F&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu5nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=f2b8a091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3076047092436334/</a><br />\n<br />\n最後：rthk32 影到有手足被臥底拘捕<br />\n<br />\n首先，扔彈的係背包紅燈標記，然後第二段片有紅燈人扔犬，被扔果班人入面有手臂帶藍，粉螢光棒的臥底（100％鬼，影住同畜龍一齊），然後唔知咩事畜龍唔見左，得臥底，開槍，手足追打臥底，最後rthk影住手足被捕。<br />\n<br />\n呢個只係從片段推測的情況。紅燈人唔可以confirm係咩水，但螢光棒一撚定係臥底，點解d畜龍唔見左，得番佢地俾手足圍，然後有手足被捕，之間發生左咩事。。。真係要靠記者或現場手足先知。萬一紅燈人係自己友，呢個方法以後已不能再用。"},{"pid":"62549fef8e9c1e02f9d873173799b3a465bd6dda","tid":1522931,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dis